organic_results.title: REQUEST FOR PROPOSAL: TICKETING SOLUTION FOR CRICKET WEST INDIES
organic_results.snippet: Cricket West Indies (CWI) is seeking a visionary, technology-powered partner to design and implement a state-of-the-art, integrated ticketing and hospitality management solution for West Indies cricket.
organic_results.snippet_extra: The RFP closes on March 15, 2025 at 5:00 PM AST.
